{"tid":732052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"☭小米☭（１８１０）暗盤收市跌４﹒７至５﹒３％","createTime":"2018-07-06T16:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T06:23:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb0de21af1f4c2434823d0fbb2322b9c0d36c2e","tid":732052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280706585\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Deditorchoice%26newsid%3DETN280706585&d=VBfUe0L1U1Z5uIZsl0533jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b004335b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280706585</a><br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社６日專訊》本港首隻「同股不同權」新股☭小米☭（０１８１０）下周一（９日）掛牌，於輝立暗盤交易場收報１６﹒１元，較招股價１７元低５﹒３％。每手２００股，若不計手續費蝕１８０元。<br />\n<br />\n　　於耀才方面，暗盤收報１６﹒２元，較招股價低４﹒７％，若不計手續費每手蝕１６０元。☭小米☭公開發售認購合共１０﹒３５億股，獲超額認購約８﹒５倍，由於僅獲輕微超額認購，一手中籤率為１００％，申請９手穩獲兩手，未錄得「頭錘飛」。<br />\n<br />\n　　國際發售股份獲輕微超額認購，配售股份最終數目為２３﹒９８億股。（ｃｈ）"},{"pid":"6fa280585e71554dc81b35f598867e9686af42b6","tid":732052,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"屌，而家周街都係d小米廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2272432b1ada0cd99471f1ee19357479b3464b03","tid":732052,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T23:57:27.000Z","msg":"佢間旗艦店幾時自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619dd353b16b00d01fb885ac7d8cde9a6f1a36fe","tid":732052,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2272432b1ada0cd99471f1ee19357479b3464b03","tid":732052,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T23:57:27.000Z","msg":"佢間旗艦店幾時自爆<img src=\"/asse